default guidance has been developed on best practice for the treatment of common chronic conditions and ﬁnancial incentives devised to 
defaultimprove the management of 
defaultchronic disease in primary care.
default1.2 
defaultA 
defaultbene
defaultﬁt of having a single payer of healthcare with universal coverage is that several years of inpatient data for the whole population are available
default and can
default be used, through time series analyses, to 
defaultexplore 
